channel.title: How to edit teles?
channel.description:
i am trying to edit the tele that is named "shops" i know the id is 29031, but i dont want it to say shops and i do not want it to tele me there. I looked in clicking.java and found the case:29031. under it says "c.triggertele(xxxx, yyyy);
Well i tried deleting that and compiled. Nothing changed. It still teleports me to the same coords. Can someone tell me how to fix that and change the name of it to " " Thanks

item.title: How to edit teles?
item.dc:creator: @kickyamom50 kickyamom50
item.description:
@kickyamom50 wrote:

Dude to change the name of the teleport, search what it originally is in “texthandler.java”, and change it, save. then to change where it teles you, teleport there, do “::mypos” then type search the coords in “clickingmost.java” or “clicking.java”. Then compile, restart your server, and it should work.
